# Group Patient SOAP Note
## List Patient SOAP Notes [/api/v1/soap_notes{?per_page}]
### List Patient SOAP Notes [GET]

Gets all the Prescriptions for the current logged in user.
Admin, Practitioner role: Gets all the prescriptions.
Patient role: Gets prescriptions assigned or created by current Patient. For this role, 'subjective', 'objective' and 'assessment' values are hidden.

+ Parameters
    + per_page: `3` (number, optional) - Enables pagination and set items per page.

+ Request Example as Practitioner

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
            X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

    + Body

