## Get Patient SOAP Note [/api/v1/soap_notes/{soap_note_id}]
### Get Patient SOAP Note [GET]

Gets an SOAP Note associated to a Patient.

+ Require Admin, Practitioner or logged in Patient matching requested patient_id. SOAP Note must belong to Patient.
+ If request is made by Patient, 'subjective', 'objective' and assessment' values are hidden.

+ Parameters
    + patient_id: `1` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.
    + soap_note_id: `3` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.

+ Request Example as Patients

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
            X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

    + Body

