## Create Patient SOAP Note [/api/v1/patients/{patient_id}/soap_notes]
### Create Patient SOAP Note [POST]

Creates an SOAP Note associated to a Patient.

+ Require Admin or Practitioner. SOAP Note will belong to Patient.

+ Parameters
    + patient_id: `1` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.

+ Request Example

    + Attributes

        + subjective: Some (string, optional) - Subjective value, 2048 characters max.
        + objective: Random (string, optional) - Objective value, 2048 characters max.
        + assessment: Test (string, optional) - Assessment value, 2048 characters max.
        + plan: String (string, optional) - Plan value, 2048 characters max.

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
            X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

    + Body

